articles.title: Germany vs. Hungary - Football Match Report - June 23, 2021 - ESPN
articles.description: Get a report of the Germany vs. Hungary 2020 European Championship, Group Stage football match.
articles.content:
Germany have edged their way into the Euro 2020 knockout stages after managing a late 2-2 draw to Hungary at the Allianz Arena in Munich on Wednesday, setting up a last 16 tie against England.
